title: Arsenal 2-1 Fulham: Did you know?
title_page: Arsenal 2-1 Fulham: Did you know? - BBC Sport
maintext: Fulham have lost successive Premier League away games for the first time since January 2024 (run of five), while they have lost three of their past five games in the competition (W2) - one more than their previous 13 games (W5 D6).
